---
title: Spaghetti Puttanesca with Avocado and Rocket Salad
description: For the days that call for pasta, make this 20-minute miracle dish your go-to. Because we’re always looking for ways to save time in the kitchen, we’ve prepared a delicious puttanesca sauce for you to add to fresh baby plum tomatoes and garlic. Served with a fresh avocado salad and topped with Italian cheese, this recipe proves that simple is often best! When you can get full on flavour in double quick time, you know you’re onto a winner!
